<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1396</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a nǐ shì quán yuán, yǒng bù zhǐ xī de quán yuán, shí shí jiāo guàn wǒ gàn kě de xīn tián,
 zhǔ nǐ shì gōng yì de rì tóu, zài wǒ de shēng mìng zhōng chū xiàn, qū zǒu wǒ xīn líng zhōng de hēi àn,
 zhǔ nǐ shì yáng de mén, zhòu yè wèi wǒ chǎng kāi, méi yǒu ràng wǒ liú luò zài wài biān,
 zhǔ nǐ shì pú táo shù wǒ shì zhī zi, yuàn yì bèi nǐ xiū jiǎn yǒng yǔ nǐ xiāng lián,
 zhǔ a nǐ shì dào lù, zhēn lǐ shēng mìng, wàn guó wàn bāng dōu xiàng nǐ sòng zàn,
 nǐ shì dé shèng de jūn wáng, nǐ shì jiù ēn de gēn yuán, nǐ de guó dù zhí dào yǒng yuǎn!</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a nǐ shì quán yuán 迦南1396</title>
</song>